00:20:23,214 --> 00:20:25,322
Pagi ini, awak kata
awak takkan datang.

332
00:20:25,347 --> 00:20:26,947
Apa yang buat awak tukar fikiran?

333
00:20:26,972 --> 00:20:28,272
Sebenarnya...

334
00:20:30,581 --> 00:20:32,881
Kenapa awak pandang ke arah Yun Seo?

335
00:20:32,906 --> 00:20:35,439
Dia sebab awak berada di sini?

336
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:37,121
