724
00:42:13,948 --> 00:42:15,481
Ketika saya dapat gaji?

725
00:42:15,881 --> 00:42:17,109
Oh Tuhan.

726
00:42:17,143 --> 00:42:19,245
Awak kata awak jadi
peguam kerana duit.

727
00:42:19,270 --> 00:42:21,490
Awak mahu suka duit, bukan?

728
00:42:25,742 --> 00:42:28,002
Cuaca terlalu sejuk.
Mari masuk ke dalam.

729
00:42:28,027 --> 00:42:30,376
Jika awak demam atau sesuatu,
saya rugi.

730
00:42:30,837 --> 00:42:32,034
Apa?

731
00:42:32,489 --> 00:42:34,182
Kenapa awak akan rugi?

732
00:42:34,528 --> 00:42:35,729
Apa?

733
00:42:37,630 --> 00:42:38,889
Awak adalah...

734
00:42:38,914 --> 00:42:40,892
