777
00:45:56,559 --> 00:45:58,853
Jika difikirkan,
awak memang sesuatu.

778
00:45:58,878 --> 00:46:00,978
Ayah awak disyaki
melakukan penipuan,

779
00:46:01,003 --> 00:46:03,903
tapi bekas teman lelaki awak
tidak mendakwa dia...

780
00:46:03,928 --> 00:46:06,208
